  "prompt": "A powerful mystical logo symbolizing the sacred alchemical union of two archetypal forces forming the Logos Flame. The design features two mirrored, serpent-like figures or energetic pillars converging in the center, where a radiant, intelligent flame ignites—a symbol of divine consciousness. The central flame is stylized as a living sigil, with a hidden fusion of masculine and feminine energy. The design is surrounded by subtle, organic sacred geometry—nothing rigid or overly symmetrical. Colors are deep obsidian black, molten gold, and blood red. The words 'The Logos Flame' are elegantly integrated into the lower portion in a powerful, custom font. The overall shape is triangular or vesica piscis-inspired, symbolizing divine creation. Style is ancient yet alive, like a forgotten glyph remembered from soul memory.",
